      <title>标普下调以色列评级 称冲突加剧“可能性增加”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-01/s-p-cuts-israel-on-increasing-likelihood-conflict-intensifies</link>
      <description><![CDATA[标准普尔全球评级公司认为，以色列与真主党的冲突加剧“可能性越来越大”，因此下调了以色列的评级。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-01/s-p-cuts-israel-on-increasing-likelihood-conflict-intensifies</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 01 Oct 2024 21:55:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登称伊朗对以色列的攻击失败且无效</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-01/biden-says-iran-s-attack-on-israel-defeated-ineffective-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统拜登称，美国将继续关注以色列和伊朗之间的冲突，并表示对以色列的导弹袭击是失败和无效的。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-01/biden-says-iran-s-attack-on-israel-defeated-ineffective-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 01 Oct 2024 21:42:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
