    <item>
      <title>Talos Energy 采取行动抵御卡洛斯·斯利姆的股票购买狂潮</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-01/talos-moves-to-defend-against-carlos-slim-s-share-buying-spree</link>
      <description><![CDATA[塔洛斯能源公司 (Talos Energy Inc.) 实施了一项所谓的毒丸计划，以抵御墨西哥亿万富翁卡洛斯·斯利姆 (Carlos Slim) 的多次股票购买，目前斯利姆的持股比例已达到 24.2%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-01/talos-moves-to-defend-against-carlos-slim-s-share-buying-spree</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 01 Oct 2024 19:09:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
